eeply into the middle to latter parts of the film because I bailed out early on . But the memory of the scenes I did see made me think that someone was doing a not - too - amusing parody of a noir movie . Sort of what Saturday Night Live has been like for the past decade : not funny . ( In my mind I kept thinking of a Guy Noir sketch , music and all . )
